title: Alesis S4 Quadrasynth
description: The Alesis S4 is the rackmount version of their Quadrasynth keyboard/synthesizer. It is a 64-voice digital synth, and is outfitted with drum kits, a high-quality processor, and an expansion card input. Also, there are four audio outputs, and features an ADAT Optical Digital Interface. The S4 is no slouch when it comes to delivering rich, varied sounds. Whether you’re looking for string sections, pianos, organs, drums, or different synthesizers, you’ll be able to find a wealth of vibrant sounds to color your sonic palette.
